after:

1. *Uzmem* knjigu sa polica. (I take the book from the shelf.)
2. *Uzeću* ti pare. (I will take you the money.)
3. *Uzela* sam novi džemper. (I took a new jumper.)
4. *Uze* ću ti nešto da jedeš. (I will take you something to eat.)
5. *Uze* li ono što mu je potrebno? (Did he take what he needed?)